    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a great car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles, this is the one! It runs beautifully and is just waiting for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
