    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance, so it\u2019s running beautifully and ready for its next adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
