    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This example boasts a linear power band facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven machine, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders.",
